ent_msg_id":"ce2b1d16-088e-44b4-8e43-2b58a7ee7015","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"ではスナップショットが `/foo/.snapshots/backup1` にあった場合は? `/foo` は消せないですよね…","ts":"1601648064.145100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"+flPu"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ec304054-ef5a-4749-871a-032d8c26c217","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"`/foo`を削除して、`/foo-snapshot`から`/foo`へのスナップショットを作りますね","ts":"1601648014.144100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Rw/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"70b4bf09-9a51-47b1-994e-9d193c50727d","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`/foo` が subvolume だったとして、 `/foo-snapshot` に `/foo` の snapshot があったとして、 `/foo` をまるごと `/foo-snapshot` で置き換えたい、って場合はどうすればいいのだろう?","ts":"1601647929.144000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Q9wJa"}]},{"client_msg_id":"0dde06c9-18aa-46d1-9a1e-3ee5faba55d9","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"subvolume だんだんわからなくなってきた…","ts":"1601647849.142600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"hFo"}]},{"client_msg_id":"8c87db7b-717a-4893-a7d7-977d54efa0e7","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"ですです、何もオプション指定しなかった時に使われるサブボリュームが切り替わる感じですね","ts":"1601647841.142500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"4XOb3"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6de58a35-86a1-4abb-a74f-0f956eac72b6","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"実はちゃんと理解してなかったのだけど、 `set-default` は本当に完全にファイルシステムルートのデフォルトサブボリュームの設定ってだけかな","ts":"1601647787.141900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"2up"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f05e9f85-9b6c-49c0-bd56-26ba1bc3b42f","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"Snapper入れるかはともかくとしてこの推奨構成はよさそう","ts":"1601647709.141100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"lQ3"}]},{"client_msg_id":"312c6f9c-cd2e-4d9e-b814-9b6656645fcf","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"あー、これ手でスナップショット置いてるサブボリュームを別にマウントする感じか、これなら確かにルート入れ替えるのでいけるか","ts":"1601647664.140500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"+9x"}]},{"client_msg_id":"72d1308e-194f-4610-b77d-9f67e1aead10","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"ロールバックの手順をどうするのかがキモかな。単に古いスナップショットからファイルをコピーしてくるだけにするのか、subvolume を set-default でガチッと過去のに切り替えちゃうのか…","ts":"1601647447.138900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"F=yW"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ff52aeff-95f9-4d59-8c2e-64c417e6dcb6","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"まあ自力でやるのそこそこめんどいので乗ってしまうのはありかな","ts":"1601647404.138100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"BMh"}]},{"client_msg_id":"5e4e7420-0b75-4ea9-8f02-c55d16d38fed","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"一通りの操作はコマンド経由でやり、スナップショット自体を直で見ない、とかならワンチャンあるかなぁと思って許容範囲内かどうかを探っている","ts":"1601647381.137300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Jk4"}]},{"client_msg_id":"954e10b0-7886-4ef7-b641-65fcc987b197","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"そう、使えはするので音楽性という言い方をしている","ts":"1601647367.137100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"O92"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a5c23dfc-bcf9-4515-8382-6178b251da3c","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"とは言え見た感じ、snapper コマンド経由でスナップショット一覧見れば日付は見れそうなんですよね","ts":"1601647325.135700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"hl7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"2843c513-9da9-4deb-80de-2504eac1770d","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"あー要らないものは外しますね","ts":"1601647301.135200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ut+7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"efce474f-8faa-41df-a5b6-30d00935a78e","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"日付にしてほしい","ts":"1601647300.135100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Di/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"df67147c-c693-477a-b5bd-c6f78dcece7f","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"わかる","ts":"1601647296.134800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/2gn"}]},{"client_msg_id":"13fc25dc-4f24-4712-935d-57095cd4c7b8","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"スナップショット番号というのが気に食わなかった","ts":"1601647292.134400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"B+e5"}]},{"client_msg_id":"485cd45e-ee57-4ba2-9395-92c2836a0a7b","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"音楽性の違いみたいなものなんでまあ","ts":"1601647269.133900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"YGz0"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f4762363-5bee-4429-8f6a-92b50a6d7d41","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"あと、 `/` (root) の snapshot を取ろうと思った場合、いらなそうな箇所(`/var/log` とか)を subvolume にして外しておくってのはどのみちやった方がよさそうなんですよねぇ","ts":"1601647269.133800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"9Gi"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b747f7ad-828e-4c6b-874b-36122e47bf79","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"それも考えてる。どっちがラクか…","ts":"1601647220.132200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"RdpQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"53f649ba-2843-4fdc-a48b-87d8d415a40b","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"従いたくなかったので全部自分で組んだやつ","ts":"1601647175.131800","team":"T03C4RC8V"